snippet: As the scheduled season approaches, Minnesota Orchestra management and the locked-out musicians seem willing to continue negotiations.
abstract: Deadline from management to settle a nearly yearlong lockout of Minnesota Orchestra players expires, even as both sides appear willing to continue negotiations.
lead_paragraph: As the scheduled season approaches, Minnesota Orchestra management and the locked-out musicians seem willing to continue negotiations.

headline.main: Deadline Passes With No End to Orchestra Labor Dispute
headline.print_headline: Deadline Passes With No End To Orchestra Labor Dispute
